<div id="more_details" class="modal fade sn-modal-size" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog ">
        <!-- Modal content-->
        <div class="modal-content sn-modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header sn-modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                <div>SHIPPING & DELIVERY INFORMATION</div>
            </div>

            <div class="">
                <ul class="nav nav-pills sn-modal-tabs sn-nav-modal-pills">
                    <li class="active"><a data-toggle="pill" href="#threshold_delivery">Threshold Delivery</a></li>
                    <li><a data-toggle="pill" href="#white_glove">WHITE GLOVE DELIVERY</a></li>
                    <li><a data-toggle="pill" href="#small_parcel">SMALL PARCEL SHIPMENT</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body sn-modal-body">
                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div id="threshold_delivery" class="tab-pane fade in active">
                        <div class="sn-modal-img-wrapper">
                          <div class="sn-modal-img">
                            <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/phonecall.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                            <div>Scheduled</div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="sn-modal-img">
                            <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/house.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                            <div>Delivered Curbside</div>
                          </div>

                        </div>

                        <p>
                          Our curbside delivery service means that your item is required to ship 3rd party freight due to one or more of your
                          items exceeding Fed Ex & UPS small parcel requirements.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Freight items do take additional time to prep for shipping and will ship within 3-7 days of placing your order if your
                            item is in stock. 3rd party freight deliveries often take 1-3 weeks to reach our service providers warehouse in your
                            area once shipped. Timeframes will vary based on your delivery area.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Once your item(s) reach our professional service providers warehouse, you will be contacted by phone to schedule
                            your curbside delivery.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            At checkout, please be sure to provide a good daytime phone number and email address so that our delivery
                            providers can reach you to schedule your delivery. Please be sure to carefully inspect your item(s) at the time of
                            delivery prior to signing and delivery documents, and notate any visible damages on the delivery documents at that
                            time.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="white_glove" class="tab-pane fade">

                      <div class="sn-modal-img-wrapper">

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/phonecall.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>Scheduled</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/house.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>In Home</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/stairs.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>Up Stairs</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/setup.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>Assembled & Placed</div>
                        </div>

                      </div>

                      <p>
                        White Glove Delivery gets you the best One of our professional service providers will contact you to schedule your
                        delivery, carefully inspect your item(s), place your items in the room of your choice, and remove all packaging
                        debris at the time of delivery.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        All white glove items require freight shipping and do take additional time to prep for shipping and will ship within
                        3-7 days of placing your order if your item is in stock. 3rd party freight deliveries often take 1-3 weeks to reach our
                        service providers warehouse in your area once shipped. Timeframes will vary based on your delivery area.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        <strong>
                          Once your item(s) reach our professional service providers warehouse, you will be contacted by phone to
                          schedule your white glove delivery.
                        </strong>
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        At checkout, please be sure to provide a good daytime phone number and email address so that our delivery
                        providers can reach you to schedule your delivery. Please be sure to carefully inspect your item(s) at the time of
                        delivery prior to signing any delivery documents, and notate any visible damages on the delivery documents at that
                        time.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="small_parcel" class="tab-pane fade">

                      <div class="sn-modal-img-wrapper">

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/smallparcel.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>Shipped Ground</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="sn-modal-img">
                          <%= image_tag 'modal_icons/house.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
                          <div>Doorstep Delivery</div>
                        </div>

                      </div>

                      <p>
                        This item will ship via UPS or Fed Ex ground as a small parcel shipment. Unless an upgraded form of
                        shipping is selected, the estimated delivery time will be 1-5 days from the date the item is shipped. This item
                        does not require a signature and will be dropped at your front door. The shipper can use their discretion to
                        require a signature when they drop your shipment. You will receive an email that contains your tracking
                        information when your item ships.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        Please note that we do not ship items to PO Boxes, Military APOâ€™s, or anywhere outside the contiguous United
                        States.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

